title: Intro: ARE YOU GARBAGE? Comedy Podcast
description: New comedy podcast from stand up comedians Kevin Ryan and H. Foley. RATE & REVIEW! Each week they sit down with a guest (mainly stand up comics) to find out if they are garbage. (HINT: Most of them are) Lots of laughs at thier expense. SUBSCRIBE!
